{"sectionId":680,"sectionIdLiteral":"680","humanId":"lesson-264","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I am surrounded by the Love of God.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 264"},"annotation":"W-264","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-264\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"680#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Father, You stand before me and behind, beside me, in the place I see myself, and everywhere I go.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>You are in all the things I look upon, the sounds I hear, and every hand that reaches for my own.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>In You time disappears, and place becomes a meaningless belief.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>For what surrounds Your Son and keeps him safe is Love itself.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>There is no source but this, and nothing is that does not share its holiness; that stands beyond Your one creation, or without the Love which holds all things within itself.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Father, Your Son is like Yourself.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>We come to You in Your Own Name today, to be at peace within Your everlasting Love.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"680#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>My brothers, join with me in this today.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>This is salvation‚Äôs prayer.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"680#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Must we not join in what will save the world, along with us?</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Father, You stand before me and behind, beside me, in the place I see myself, and everywhere I go. You are in all the things I look upon, the sounds I hear, and every hand that reaches for my own. In","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 264: I am surrounded by the Love of God | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†264 ‚ÄúI am surrounded by the Love of God‚Äù: Father, You stand before me and behind, beside me, in the place I see myself,‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"5. What Is the Body?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":676,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-body"]}},{"label":"Lesson 264","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":680,"slugs":["lesson-264","i-am-surrounded-by-the-love-of-god"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"5. What Is the Body?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":676,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-body"]}},{"label":"Lesson 264","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":680,"slugs":["lesson-264","i-am-surrounded-by-the-love-of-god"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"5. What Is the Body?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":676,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-body"]}},{"label":"Lesson 264","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":680,"slugs":["lesson-264","i-am-surrounded-by-the-love-of-god"]}}],"